<commentary>etad eva darśayati.

raktaṃ dviṣṭaṃ vā svacittaṃ yadā paśyet, tadā hastapādādicalanamātram api na kartavyam, nāpi vacanodīraṇam. anyathā tadutthāpite kāyavāgvijñapty api saṃkliṣṭe syātām. ato bahirindriyavyāpāravikalpāv upasaṃhṛtya sthātavyaṃ kāṣṭhavat tadā. sarvavyāpāravirahān nirvyāpārāḥ sarvadharmā iti manasi nidhāya.</commentary>

aparam āha. uddhatam iti saddharmādiśravaṇapramādād api uddhatam, vikṣepabahulam ity arthaḥ. sopahāsaṃ vāgviheṭhanārambhakaṃ tayā yuktaṃ vā. mānaś cittasyonnatiḥ. madaḥ svadharme cittasyābhiniveśaḥ.